        date_read: "2023-12-31",
        book_notes: "<p>I first happened upon the practice of Zhan Zhuang through a Channel Four (UK) program hosted by Master Lam Kam-Chueng. Spotted the videos on YouTube&trade; last year. Mark Cohen's book has lots of practical insights. Learning about the WHY is giving me a good reason to continue my practice.</p>\r\n<p>Cohen has written a follow-up book entitled \"Deeper Into Zhan Zhuang\".</p>",
